org.jetel.component.tree.writer.util

Class AbstractVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jetel.component.tree.writer.util.AbstractVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MappingVisitor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractMappingValidator, MappingCompiler, MappingTagger

    public abstract class AbstractVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
implements MappingVisitor
    This visitor handles referencing templates, simulates expanding and prevents infinite loops when templates are used in recursive way.
